prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover, dynamic comic book style. A superhero scene featuring cartoon versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo. Lao Lao, as the main superhero, is in the foreground, striking a powerful and funny pose. She wears a stylized, vibrant version of her white dress from the photo, now with a flowing cape and a fun superhero mask. She's joyfully holding a giant, comically oversized birthday cupcake with a single lit candle. Jordan, also as a cartoon superhero in a simplified version of his graduation gown without any text, is in the background, slightly smaller, cheering her on with an amazed expression and giving two thumbs up. The background is a burst of bright, explosive comic book "POW!" and "ZAP!" graphics in yellow, red, and blue, with dynamic speed lines radiating from the center. The entire scene has bold black outlines, vibrant flat colors, and uses Ben-Day dots for shading to complete the classic comic book feel. In the center, within a stylized comic book speech bubble, the text "Happy Birthday, Super Lao Lao!" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. 2D flat illustration for printing.
